snippet.title: OMORI: MARI IS HOME Proof of Concept/Trailer (MOD)
snippet.description:
Trailer/Proof of Concept for the OMORI Mod "MARI IS HOME", which takes place after the good ending.
Footage shown is not final and subject to change/polishing.

If this is of interest to you, you can join the Discord server here: https://discord.gg/kFDVAac4Q5
